          "settings": {
            "comments_title": "<p>@Sean</p>",
            "comments_small_title": "<p>Dartmouth, CA</p>",
            "comments_text": "<p>“You need to have a bit of technical skill, and be willing to do some problem solving, but I can certainly help to get you over most humps, if they come up.”</p>",
